---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
import BookingButton from '../components/BookingButton.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="New Patients"
  description="Plan your first visit with Dr. Colin MacLeod, ND in Bedford. Learn how appointments and private blood testing work, what to prepare, current fees and how to book."
  focusKeyword="new patient naturopathic appointment Bedford NS"
>
  <HeroSection title="Your First Visit" centered compact>
    How the first appointment works, what to prepare and what your options may cost.
    <div slot="cta" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 pt-2">
      <BookingButton text="Book Online" variant="hero" size="lg" source="new-patients-hero" />
      <a
        href="#blood-testing"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Coming for Blood Work?
        <svg class="ml-2 h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </HeroSection>

  <!-- Private blood testing pathway -->
  <section id="blood-testing" class="scroll-mt-28 bg-emerald-50 py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:items-center reveal">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-emerald-700">Private Laboratory Access</p>
          <h2 class="mb-5 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 sm:text-4xl">Coming for Blood Work?</h2>
          <p class="mb-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
            Book an initial consultation if you would like private blood testing. The appointment provides time to review your concerns, previous results, medications and the tests you would like to explore.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
            Dr. MacLeod can help select a broad set of relevant markers, explain what each test can and cannot show, and arrange a private laboratory requisition and in-office collection. Testing costs are separate from the consultation fee and are confirmed before proceeding.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-emerald-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
          <h3 class="mb-5 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">A simple place to start</h3>
          <ol class="space-y-5">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-800">1</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">Book an initial consultation</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">No family-doctor or specialist referral is required for private testing.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-800">2</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">Bring any previous results</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Existing blood work and reports help identify what has already been assessed and where broader testing may be useful.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-sm font-bold text-emerald-800">3</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">Review the plan and costs</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">The selected tests, preparation instructions and laboratory fees are reviewed before collection is arranged.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <a href="/lab-testing/" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition-colors hover:text-emerald-950">
            Explore Lab Testing
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Visit process -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl reveal">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-3xl text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 sm:text-4xl">How Your First Visit Works</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">The initial appointment is a 60-minute review of your health concerns, history, previous results, medications and priorities.</p>
        </div>

        <ol class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
          <li class="relative border-t border-emerald-200 pt-7">
            <span class="absolute -top-5 left-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-900 text-sm font-bold text-white ring-8 ring-white">1</span>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">Prepare</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Complete the requested intake information and gather any previous laboratory results, imaging or reports you would like reviewed.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="relative border-t border-emerald-200 pt-7">
            <span class="absolute -top-5 left-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-900 text-sm font-bold text-white ring-8 ring-white">2</span>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">Meet</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Discuss your symptoms, health history, current care and goals. There is time to address the concerns and testing priorities that brought you in.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="relative border-t border-emerald-200 pt-7">
            <span class="absolute -top-5 left-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-900 text-sm font-bold text-white ring-8 ring-white">3</span>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">Plan the Next Step</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Review appropriate testing or treatment options, their limitations and costs. Follow-up visits are used to review results and adjust the plan when needed.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>

        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-3 border-t border-emerald-100 pt-7 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <span><strong class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">Initial consultation:</strong> 60 minutes</span>
          <span><strong class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">Follow-up visit:</strong> 30 minutes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Preparation checklist -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.7fr_1.3fr] lg:items-start reveal">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-emerald-300">Before Your Appointment</p>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-white sm:text-4xl">What to Prepare</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-emerald-100">Bring what you have access to. You do not need a perfectly organized medical file before booking.</p>
        </div>

        <ul class="grid gap-x-10 gap-y-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Health history</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-100">Past conditions, surgeries and hospitalizations, with approximate dates when possible.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Medications and supplements</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-100">A current list of prescriptions, over-the-counter medications, vitamins and supplements.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Previous results</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-100">Relevant blood work, imaging and diagnostic reports you already have available.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <div><h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Insurance details</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-100">Your extended health insurance information if you would like the clinic to attempt direct billing.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fees and insurance -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl reveal">
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 sm:text-4xl">Fees & Insurance</h2>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Consultation fees, private laboratory charges and treatment costs are billed separately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 bg-emerald-50/50">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:border-r md:border-emerald-100">
              <h3 class="mb-5 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">Visit Fees</h3>
              <dl class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-emerald-100 pb-4">
                  <dt>Initial consultation <span class="block text-sm text-slate-500">60 minutes</span></dt>
                  <dd class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">$200</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                  <dt>Follow-up visit <span class="block text-sm text-slate-500">30 minutes</span></dt>
                  <dd class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">$100</dd>
                </div>
              </dl>
              <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Laboratory, IV therapy, prolotherapy and other treatment costs vary. Any additional costs are reviewed before testing or treatment proceeds.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-emerald-100 p-6 sm:p-8 md:border-t-0">
              <h3 class="mb-5 text-xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950">Insurance & Payment</h3>
              <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed text-slate-700">Many extended health plans include naturopathic services. Coverage limits and eligibility vary, so please confirm the details of your individual plan.</p>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
                <li class="flex gap-3"><svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Direct insurance billing is available where supported.</li>
                <li class="flex gap-3"><svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Credit and debit cards, cash and e-transfer are accepted.</li>
                <li class="flex gap-3"><svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-none text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Receipts are provided for reimbursement claims.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="border-t border-emerald-100 bg-white px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">Please provide at least <strong class="font-semibold text-slate-700">24 hours' notice</strong> to cancel or reschedule an appointment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Finding the clinic -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-50 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-14 reveal">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-xl">
          <img
            src="/images/general/ihpc-building.webp"
            alt="Integrated Health Professional Centre at 1378 Bedford Highway, Unit 1"
            class="aspect-[16/10] w-full object-cover"
            width="1600"
            height="972"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-emerald-700">Plan Your Arrival</p>
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-emerald-950 sm:text-4xl">Finding the Clinic</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">Optimal Wellbeing Clinic is located inside the Integrated Health Professional Centre at 1378 Bedford Highway, Unit 1, in Bedford.</p>
          <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-600">The building has accessible facilities and on-site parking. Look for the Integrated Health Professional Centre signage when you arrive.</p>
          <a
            href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=1378+Bedford+Highway,+Unit+1,Bedford,NS,Canada"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition-colors hover:text-emerald-950"
          >
            Get Directions
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing CTA -->
  <section class="bg-emerald-950 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="section-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center reveal">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-serif font-medium text-white sm:text-4xl">Ready to Book?</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-emerald-100">Book online anytime through the secure patient portal, or call the clinic during office hours.</p>
        <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
          <BookingButton text="Book Online" variant="hero" size="lg" source="new-patients" />
          <a href="tel:+19024064424" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-white/10">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
            (902) 406-4424
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-emerald-200"><strong>Optimal Wellbeing Clinic</strong> &bull; 1378 Bedford Highway, Unit 1, Bedford &bull; Mon-Fri: 7:30 AM-3:30 PM</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
